name: Webby's Jump
description:
Webby the Fly has escaped the grasps of his evil spider captors! Relatively unscathed, his legs will do what his wings cannot - get him as far away from the spiders as possible!

Created for Mini Jam 123: "Web"

Bounce as high as you can on any modern web browser. 

Controls:

Tap/Click on the left half of the screen, or use the Left Arrow/A keys to move left.

Tap/Click on the right half of the screen, or use the Right Arrow/D keys to move right.

To save your score to the online leaderboards please ensure you've typed in your initials, clicked the 'tick', and then accessed the leaderboards via the button below.

Mute button does work, you just need to tap it twice the first time.
